aiohttp-sse
===========
.. image:: https://github.com/aio-libs/aiohttp-sse/workflows/CI/badge.svg?event=push
    :target: https://github.com/aio-libs/aiohttp-sse/actions?query=event%3Apush+branch%3Amaster

